---
title: Roasted Root Veggie & Lentil Salad with Caramelised Walnuts, Feta & Dijon Dressing
description: We toyed with calling this delish little salad ‘Fruits of the Forest’ because we’re whimsical and a little bit ridiculous if we’re being honest. But come on! This winning combo of nuts, feta and root veggies will have you feeling a bit Disney-princess-with- a-forest-animal-sidekick too.

*Keep an eye out...Due to recent sourcing challenges, we’ve replaced orange kumara with red kumara, which may be a little different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
